tool_description: Let's create animated GIF from base64 images. This API will convert base64 images into an animated GIF image. You need to provide base64 lists of images and API will return the base64 of result animated GIF image.
name: base64Images2Gif
title: base64Images2Gif

api_list.name: base64toGIFbase64
api_list.description: This API will convert **base64 images** into an animated GIF image. You need to provide base64 lists of images and API will return the **base64 of result GIF image**.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://base64images2gif.p.rapidapi.com/image2Gif-prod-hello"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "base64images2gif.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
